# TideFS xfstests exclude list for FUSE preview baseline
#
# Tests excluded because they require features not yet in the tidefs FUSE adapter.
# Format: one test pattern per line. Comments start with #.
# Tag legend: [ACL] [CAP] [ENCRYPT] [IMMUTABLE] [IOCTL] [KERNEL] [MMAP] [QUOTA] [SWAP] [TIMESTAMPS]
#
# Removed as delivered:
#   file locks (#491/#791): generic/131, generic/150, generic/167
#   FIEMAP (#500): generic/317
#   O_DIRECT (#876): generic/095, generic/130, generic/208-213, generic/240
#   sub-second timestamps (#3184): generic/258 (atimensec/mtimensec/ctimensec confirmed
#     wired through full FUSE attr path — fuse_vfs_adapter.rs:782-784,839-841)
#   special-node mknod: generic/184

# --- ACLs ---
#   ACL evaluation IS wired via tidefs-posix-acl + tidefs-permission check_access()
#   (fuse_preview.rs:759-796,2029-2048). These exclusions remain until the full ACL
#   xfstests suite (set/get/inherit/default) is verified passing end-to-end.
